• we’re helping podia hire a community marketer. this is a really cool role. <https://superpath.co/job/9-community-marketer-podia|learn more here> and feel free to dm <@UJWJLLD63> with questions.

hope you are all having a good day!

attachments.text: Hi everyone! Thanks so much for contributing to this year’s salary survey. I’ll plan to conduct this every year in January for the previous year. You can take a look at last year’s here [<https://docs.google.com/document/d/1M7ENZThZrdqxOpXvTgjeYJItHzdlHxm-tLcPikEZUhk/edit>] . A few things about this data: * It’s a small sample size (81 respondents). It’s obviously not comprehensive, but I do think the findings can be a valuable tool for negotiating salaries/raises and setting freelance r
